cMonkey Python - Python port of the cMonkey biclustering algorithm

This is the Python implementation of the cMonkey algorithm.

-- Wei-ju Wu, Institute for Systems Biology, July 2011

Original R implementation by David Reiss, Institute for Systems Biology

Status
------
The project is still in an early development phase.

System requirements
-------------------
- Developed and tested with Python 2.7.2
- scipy >= 0.9.0
- numpy >= 1.6.0
- BeautifulSoup >= 3.2.0

To run the unit tests:

./run_tests.sh (for TDD)
./run_integration_tests.sh (slow, run occacionally)

There is a startup script for cMonkey to run the current integrated
system

./run_cmonkey.sh

